<p>
If you are a C/C++ programmer like me, you may experience jumping around different machines to write and compile your code, or you may write code on different machines for different projects, and scp/rsync/ftp the projects around. It works, but it&#39;s a bit tedious and takes too much burden on our brains.</p>
